Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're told Mr Matsumoto is a fearless person, but can you narrate\Nto us the most life-threatening situation you've been in so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fade(334,0)\t(0,0,\fscx120,\fscy120)\pos(192,180.4)}The Old Man and the Gorilla
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,did the guy actually call you "fearless"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see now, the most dangerous experience I've had till now would be....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...I guess it'd have to be the time I was whacked by a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,around here.....it went BAM!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant where were you when this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,well let's see...I was playing baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,WHERE!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in the field, in the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see now - it was the Amagasaki baseball\Nfield (Matsumoto and Hamada's hometown in Hyogo prefecture)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,huh! You've never told me this story before!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?...(politely)..well, can you please listen anyway.....?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wham! You remember, I used to hit homeruns all the time back then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, if you say so...(stiffening up out of respect) - aye,aye cap'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my adolescence was all about homeruns, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what're you, an idiot?....enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wham!!!   Man, did I strike the ball hard back in the day!...SMASHED it\Nclear out of the field, and it broke the glass in someone's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so I make my way over there to apologize....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I got there, there he was....the Gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,really? a Gorilla? you don't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...actually, there was an old man too....AND a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it, the gorilla was with the old\Nman at his place! I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, 'What do you plan to do about this window kid? I\Njust replaced the glass after it was broken a while back!'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And through it all the gorilla was like this...(sways and swaggers about menacingly)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a yankee punk gorilla staring at you up and down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I was like all...bowing down low...being humble, you know?...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,....just genuflecting and flopping before the guy, you know?....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also just a kid back then, remember?....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And just then, the gorilla pushes the old man aside....and....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,wow! he stepped out in front of him, did he?......and?....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,'Why the hell don't you just apologize punk?!'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,wait...hold on a second here....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(gestures: 'aren't you getting ahead of the story here?')
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The gorilla spoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's what the old man said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah, I get you now -  had me going there for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...no, it was the old man, of course....(chuckles to\Nhimself at the idea of a gorilla talking)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks, ok i get it now... startled me there for a minute....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the old man asked me why I wouldn't apologize....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,....and then it was like,'Oi, oi, oi, oi!'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,wait, wait, wait, hold on a minute again!..the\Ngorilla threatened you with,'Oi, oi, oi, oi?'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,no, no, that was the old man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,aaah, i got you -  so it was the old man talking again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,.....wow...the old guy sure has a lot to say, didn't he?...and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well, so the old man was like,'Oi, oi, oi, oi!'...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was humbly like,'Well, I don't see why I should apologize,\Nsince I will definitely compensate you for the damage done.'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,....and when I said that, it just stepped out menacingly and was like,'YOU\NTHINK COMPENSATING FOR THE DAMAGE IS GOING TO MAKE EVERYTHING OK?!?!'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wait, wait, wait, hold on just a minute again!...this was the goril.....?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,no, no, it was still the old man, the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, i get it - so it was the old man again...........the old\Nguy sure keeps stepping out into the front a lot, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With the old guy stepping out so many times, you'd think the poor gorilla would start to feel cramped and crowded out - he'd think\N'Should I just squeeze myself to the front from the side somehow? Why doesn't the old geezer just get out of the way?'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it was like......BAMMM!!!......I don't know if it was a big rock or a\Ndesk lying around or something that was dashed to the ground...and it said....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!...and then?....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,'DO YOU THINK YOU CAN FUCK WITH A GORILLA AND GET AWAY WITH IT?!?!'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,eh?..stop!...wait, wait a minute....was this the gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,no, no, the old man, the old man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then ......(in a soft voice) 'just compensate us for the damage'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT was the gorilla speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so THAT was the gorilla speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time, the gorilla spoke
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty chilled out gorilla! - not in the habit of getting angry is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He just says softly,'Compensate us for the damage'!....oooooh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you in the least bit startled when the gorilla started speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that part didn't startle me, not really!...I was\Na wild and reckless guy back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But really....isn't it odd and funny?....I mean why should anyone have to apologize...if you\Ncompensate for the damage, that should be the end of story, right?.......
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like, 'You bruised me right here in my arm!'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you injured the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was once again the gorilla I'm talking about....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the gorilla addressed you formally and said, 'You have injured me!'.....?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he walks up all of a sudden, and....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that must have been scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have been around this tall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, he was a big, tall gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,BAM!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, did it break your jaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was the OLD MAN who got whacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't they living together happily all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,'That's how much destructiveness I have pent up!'............
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,..........was what the old man finally said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a strange, scary day it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one whacked or even touched you!

